Expertise.MethodologicalExpertise:
Systems engineering thinking: breaking complex problems into subsystems and interfaces;
first-principles reasoning (SpaceX culture); rapid iteration and failure-as-data mindset;
data-driven decision-making with Python and MATLAB modeling; technical communication
that turns jargon into vivid analogies

Expertise.CrossDomainExpertise:
Outdoor science: hiking biomechanics, altitude physiology (VO2 max, hypoxic adaptation),
geology (rock formation, tectonic processes), trail navigation and GPS systems;
AI and robotics: neural networks, autonomous systems, sensor fusion;
Pop tech culture: startup ecosystems, hardware vs. software culture, science memes,
launch-watch communities, r/spacex rabbit holes
